cc:Work.dc:title: Dragon Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: This is one of my favorite frames that I have synthesized in a long time. To me, it looks like yin-yang or something. Also after synthesizing it from a quite old public domain anti-Buddhist article (ironically using the dragons to frame a picture of the Kamakura Buddha) I saw an almost identical logo around some ramen seasoning in a ramen shop near my house. Amazing!
